y references to OAuth2WebClient may fail due to missing imported types. However, even without dependencies, existing tests are already meaningful, so they might not require this new dependency.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering docker image**\\n\\nI'm thinking about whether a Docker image is needed, but it seems like that's not the case. Instead, a local HTTP server might be more appropriate. I wonder if I should reference the normal usage documentation to ensure clarity. It would make sense to keep the final explanation concise while highlighting important details. Keeping things straightforward will help avoid confusion and ensure the user understands the setup without unnecessary complexity.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Vert.x Web Client 5.0.1 remains a local HTTP client/server test target with no Docker service or extra mandatory dependency, but its Netty 4.2.2.Final runtime needs the same Java 24+/25 unsafe-access native runtime properties already used for 5.0.0.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For native test execution of io.vertx:vertx-web-client:5.0.1, configure runtime system properties/args: -Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true. Meaningful tests can use Vertx.vertx(), WebClient/WebClientSession/CachingWebClient, BodyCodec, local 127.0.0.1 HttpServer endpoints, JSON/forms/multipart/streaming, redirects, cookies, and cache headers; no external service is required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The existing 5.0.0 test scaffold applies these native runtime args only when libraryVersion == '5.0.0', so running the 5.0.1 candidate through that scaffold can omit them.\",\n    \"io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2:5.0.1 is an optional artifact only needed if tests intentionally exercise OAuth2WebClient; it is not required for core WebClient coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05a00aab0cc7cb94016a4200d591a4819495d162ae8056fcb8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1266, "output": 817, "cacheRead": 29184, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 31267, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782710476135, "responseId": "resp_05a00aab0cc7cb94016a4200cc93b48194ae559fb834072514"}, "toolResults": []}
